{"tid":471170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"哥倫比亞巨乳老師強逼學生性交","createTime":"2017-11-17T04:02:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-17T05:58:00.000Z","uid":54747,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"70dbad35d5bb8470a887f813c1d4838aca40cba3","tid":471170,"uid":54747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T04:02:10.000Z","msg":"哥倫比亞一名40歲高中女老師優卡塔(Yokasta M)，是位人妻，但也是位淫蕩女教師，她逼迫學生若不跟她上床，就要當掉學生。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《每日郵報》報導，優卡塔利用課堂機會物色多位16~17歲小鮮肉男高生，並透過社群軟體接近他們，還說要給他們「特殊性教育」，並獲得學生們的電話和其他聯絡方式。優卡塔之後對他們傳情色貼圖與簡訊，甚至逼迫他們上床，威脅「不做愛就當掉」，多位男生因此唯命是從。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據悉優卡塔跟男生們發生性關係的時間，是在去年1~4月，但這起事件會爆發，是因為一位學生的爸爸在近日看到兒子的手機內，有多張優卡塔的情色照片，這名父親因而報警。目前優卡塔已被逮捕，她恐面臨40年徒刑，老公也跟她離婚。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/17/120138_34eea2e7399c23ca5785bae0518dd923.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2F120138_34eea2e7399c23ca5785bae0518dd923.jpg&h=2ccf55cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"50193432b20ec668613fa6a377d8d83ed32727b6","tid":471170,"uid":85557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T04:05:34.000Z","msg":"40路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a982c6cad819d6a445cc2e3c9fdc2d7e6344550","tid":471170,"uid":54747,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T04:07:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/17/120659_9280f2971ded58ce9a2fee40bff4426b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F17%2F120659_9280f2971ded58ce9a2fee40bff4426b.jpg&h=0ea45a41&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76c4136cf9abd3c69bd0159145ae9292e5f7e0fa","tid":471170,"uid":119366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T04:07:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img s